Package: BRRAT
Title: Bayesian Regression Robustness Assessment Test
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Matt", "Gibbs", email = "matt.gibbs@csiro.au",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/matt-s-gibbs/SWTools
Description: Tests for a linear relationship log ratio errors between an observed and simulated series
    and an independent variable. Typically this the error in modelled streamflow at an annual time scale, and a rainfall
    input. The approach allows for multiple sites as random factors and for multiple replicates of the simulated values.
    The approach is outlined in Gibbs et al. (2025).
